(aus dI qwkq) dw koeI h`d-bMnw nhIN hY[
(isRStI nUM Awpxy) hukm ivc pYdw kr ky ibnw iksy Awsry itkw r`Kdw hY,
(jgq aus dy) hukm ivc pYdw huMdw hY qy hukm ivc lIn ho jWdw hY[
au~cy qy nIvyN bMidAW dI vrqoN BI aus dy hukm ivc hI hY,
AnykW iksmW dy Kyf-qmwSy aus dy hukm ivc ho rhy hn[
AwpxI bzurgI (dy kMm) kr kr ky Awp hI vyK irhw hY[
hy nwnk! pRBU sB jIvW ivc ivAwpk hY ]1]
jy pRBU nUM cMgI l`gy qW mnu`K nUM au~cI Awqmk AvsQw dyNdw hY,
Aqy p`Qr (-idlW) nUM BI qwr lYNdw hY[
jy pRBU cwhy qW suAwsW qoN ibnw BI pRwxI nUM (mOq qoN) bcw r`Kdw hY,
aus dI myhr hovy qW jIv pRBU dy gux gwauNdw hY[
jy Akwl purK dI rzw hovy qW igry hoey cln vwilAW nUM (ivkwrW qoN) bcw lYNdw hY;
jo kuJ krdw hY, AwpxI slwh Anuswr krdw hY[
pRBU Awp hI lok prlok dw mwlk hY,
auh sB dy idl dI jwxn vwlw Awp jgq-Kyf Kyfdw hY qy (ies nUM vyK ky) ^uS huMdw hY[
jo aus nUM cMgw l`gdw hY auhI kMm krdw hY[
hy nwnk! (aus vrgw) koeI hor nhIN id`sdw ]2]
d`so, mnu`K pwsoN (Awpxy Awp) kyhVw kMm ho skdw hY?
jo pRBU nUM cMgw l`gdw hY, auhI (jIv pwsoN) krwauNdw hY[
ies (mnu`K) dy v`s hovy qW hryk cIz sWB ley,
(pr) pRBU auhI kuJ krdw hY jo aus nUM BwauNdw hY[
mUrKqw dy kwrx mnu`K mwieAw ivc ru`J jWdw hY,
jy smJ vwlw hovy qW Awpxy Awp (ies qoN) bicAw rhy;
(pr ies dw mn) BulyKy ivc Bu`lw hoieAw (mwieAw dI ^wiqr) dsIN pwsIN dOVdw hY,
A`K dy Por ivc chuM kUtW ivc B`j dOV AwauNdw hY[
(pRBU) myhr kr ky ijs ijs mnu`K nUM AwpxI BgqI b^Sdw hY,
hy nwnk! auh mnu`K nwm ivc itky rihMdy hn ]3]
iKx ivc pRBU kIVy (vrgy) nIvyN (mnu`K) nUM rwj dy dyNdw hY,
pRBU ZrIbW qy myhr krn vwlw hY[
ijs mnu`K dw koeI gux nhIN id`s AwauNdw,
aus nUM plk ivc dsIN pwsIN au~Gw kr dyNdw hY[
ijs mnu`K qy jgq dw mwlk pRBU AwpxI b^SS krdw hY;
aus dw (krmW dw) lyKw nhIN igxdw[
ieh ijMd qy srIr sB aus pRBU dI id`qI hoeI pUMjI hY,
hryk srIr ivc ivAwpk pRBU dw hI jlvw hY[
ieh (jgq-) rcnw aus ny Awp rcI hY[
hy nwnk! AwpxI (ies) bzurgI nUM Awp vyK ky ^uS ho irhw hY ]4]
ies (jIv) dI qwkq ies dy Awpxy h`Q nhIN hY,
sB jIvW dw mwlk pRBU Awp sB kuJ krn krwaux dy smr`Q hY[
ivcwrw jIv pRBU dy hukm ivc hI qurn vwlw hY,
(ikauNik) huMdw EhI hY jo aus pRBU nUM BwauNdw hY[
(pRBU Awp) kdy au~icAW ivc kdy nIivAW ivc pRgt ho irhw hY,
kdy icMqw ivc hY qy kdy KuSI dI mOj ivc h`s irhw hY;
kdy (dUijAW dI) inMidAw ivcwrn dw ivhwr bxweI bYTw hY,
kdy (^uSI dy kwrx) AkwS ivc au~cw (cVHdw hY) (kdy icMqw dy kwrx) pqwl ivc (if`gw ipAw hY);
